&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This position currently offers an onsite work schedule, with the expectation that you are in the office four (4) days per week during onsite core days.&amp;nbsp; Our current onsite core days are Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, and Thursday.&amp;nbsp; The work schedule type and core days are subject to change with advance notification and manager discretion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
