&lt;li&gt;Arrange travel, accommodations, itineraries and all correspondence related to necessary arrangements including management of expense reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan, organize and execute events such as meetings, team building activities, luncheons, client dinners and special projects&lt;/li&gt;
