&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with distribution leaders, field leaders, wholesalers and agency partners to promote our key advanced market strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand life insurance and annuity products. A plus if there is an understanding of NLG products and illustration software.&lt;/li&gt;
