&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will contribute to the pricing and structuring of reinsurance deals, assess the capital impact of strategic transactions, and help manage NLG’s economic, regulatory capital frameworks. This position requires strong technical modeling ability, sound actuarial judgment, and the ability to communicate complex results to both actuarial and non-actuarial audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position currently offers an onsite hybrid work schedule, with the expectation that you are in the office four (4) days per week during onsite core days. Our current onsite core days are Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, and Thursday.&amp;nbsp; The work schedule type and core days are subject to change with advance notification and manager discretion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can be based on Vermont or Dallas Campus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
