&lt;li&gt;Quantify the impact of deals and capital actions across multiple frameworks (e.g., statutory, GAAP, economic capital, RBC).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development of pricing analyses and scenario testing for prospective reinsurance or financing structures, including legal entity modeling, cash-flow projections, sensitivities, and stress tests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with MCOE, Finance, Pricing and related business areas to align modeling assumptions, capital methodologies, and reinsurance transaction structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and enhance actuarial models to assess capital usage, return on capital, and value creation for reinsurance transactions, M&amp;amp;A opportunities, and other capital or risk-transfer strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
