&lt;li&gt;Work with internal partners to accurately capture RBC and S&amp;amp;P capital impacts of proposed capital strategies, including reinsurance, non-admitted assets, and block sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support for capital management, board, and IRC meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform ad hoc analysis as requested to determine impacts on current and future capital positions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All other duties as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
