&lt;li&gt;Lead tax forecasting, effective tax rate analysis, and other ad hoc tax reporting and modeling needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee federal, state, and local income tax compliance, including return preparation, review, filing coordination, and return-to-provision analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review tax deliverables, improve processes, and strengthen internal controls to support accuracy, efficiency, and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage external tax advisors to ensure timely, high-quality, and cost-effective tax engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support tax planning initiatives by identifying opportunities to optimize the company’s tax position and mitigate risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct technical tax research and provide guidance on compliance, reporting, and business matters.&lt;/li&gt;
