&lt;p&gt;The Director, Advanced Analytics &amp;amp; Governance is a senior leadership role within the Chief Data Office responsible for driving the continued maturation of the organization’s analytics and reporting capabilities and for advancing enterprise-wide analytics standards. In this role, you will lead a team of data analysts, analytics engineers, reporting governance specialists, and data stewards to deliver high-impact solutions while ensuring data is trusted, secure, compliant, and governed effectively across the enterprise. You’ll operate at the intersection of business, analytics, and technology — bridging technical innovation in advanced analytics with robust data governance, privacy, and ethical standards.&lt;/p&gt;
